msgid "Record this pastoral follow-up for the whole family"
msgstr "Catatlah tindak lanjut pastoral ini untuk seluruh keluarga"

msgid "Pastoral follow-up recorded"
msgstr "Tindak lanjut pastoral dicatat"

msgid "Error"
msgstr "Kesalahan"

msgid "Unable to record pastoral follow-up."
msgstr "Tidak dapat mencatat tindak lanjut pastoral."

msgid "Confirm Deactivation"
msgstr "Konfirmasi Penonaktifan"

msgid "Confirm Activation"
msgstr "Konfirmasi Aktivasi"

msgid "You are about to deactivate this person:"
msgstr "Anda akan menonaktifkan orang ini:"

msgid "You are about to deactivate this family:"
msgstr "Anda akan menonaktifkan keluarga ini:"

msgid "You are about to reactivate this person:"
msgstr "Anda akan mengaktifkan kembali orang ini:"

msgid "You are about to reactivate this family:"
msgstr "Anda akan mengaktifkan kembali keluarga ini:"

msgid ""
"For GDPR reasons, make sure you have the person's agreement before "
"reactivating their record."
msgstr ""
"Untuk alasan GDPR, pastikan Anda mendapatkan persetujuan dari orang tersebut "
"sebelum mengaktifkan kembali catatan mereka."

msgid ""
"For GDPR reasons, make sure you have the agreement of the family members "
"before reactivating their record."
msgstr ""
"Untuk alasan GDPR, pastikan Anda mendapatkan persetujuan dari anggota "
"keluarga sebelum mengaktifkan kembali catatan mereka."

msgid "Privacy reminder"
msgstr "Pengingat privasi"

msgid "Also deactivate the whole family"
msgstr "Juga menonaktifkan seluruh keluarga"

msgid ""
"Use this if the entire household should be marked as inactive at the same "
"time."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan ini jika seluruh rumah tangga harus ditandai sebagai tidak aktif "
"pada saat yang sama."

msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "Batal"

msgid "Confirm deactivation"
msgstr "Konfirmasi penonaktifan"

msgid "Confirm activation"
msgstr "Konfirmasi aktivasi"

msgid "Unable to update this person status."
msgstr "Tidak dapat memperbarui status orang ini."

msgid "Unable to update this family status."
msgstr "Tidak dapat memperbarui status keluarga ini."

msgid "Pastoral Care Note Creation"
msgstr "Pembuatan Catatan Perawatan Pastoral"

msgid "Close"
msgstr "Tutup"

msgid "Save"
msgstr "Simpan"

msgid "Unable to load the pastoral follow-up editor."
msgstr "Tidak dapat memuat editor tindak lanjut pastoral."
